name: UW-Women in IT (UW-WIT) and Carrie Regenstein Networking Event
description: Join UW-WIT in welcoming Carrie Regenstein with conversation and light refreshments, as we continue building our community of support for improving the environment for women in IT at UW-Madison and beyond. This event will directly follow the discussion event, “Preparing for the Next Opportunity: Developing Staff and Yourself in Lean Times.” Separate registration is required.
